01:44.805 --> 01:47.139
Do not hide your face from me.

01:47.141 --> 01:50.642
Do not let me be like the dead
who go down to the underworld.

01:50.644 --> 01:52.177
Amen.

02:32.785 --> 02:35.587
It is the group that defines us,

02:35.589 --> 02:37.756
that gives us meaning,

02:37.758 --> 02:40.826
belonging, a sense
of a common goal.

02:40.828 --> 02:42.694
We are born alone and die alone.

02:42.696 --> 02:45.364
But in this journey,

02:45.366 --> 02:48.667
we are given the chance
to walk the path together

02:48.669 --> 02:51.737
<i>instead of wandering in
the mist like lost sheep.</i>

02:51.739 --> 02:53.672
Body of Christ.

02:53.674 --> 02:55.240
Amen.

02:55.242 --> 02:57.576
<i>Now, if we are
to become a flock,</i>

02:57.578 --> 02:59.478
<i>if that is our true destiny,</i>

02:59.480 --> 03:01.713
<i>who then is our true shepherd?</i>

03:05.485 --> 03:08.587
<i>I believe it is the one
who will deliver us</i>

03:08.589 --> 03:10.656
<i>to the green meadows</i>

03:10.658 --> 03:13.192
instead of the slaughterhouse.

03:18.231 --> 03:19.698
Through the ministry
of the Church,

03:19.700 --> 03:21.800
may God give you
pardon and peace.

03:21.802 --> 03:23.802
I absolve you from your sins.

03:23.804 --> 03:26.605
In the name of the Father and
of the Son and the Holy Spirit.

03:26.607 --> 03:27.940
Amen.

03:27.942 --> 03:29.441
You are now freed
from your sins.

03:29.443 --> 03:30.509
Go in peace.

03:30.511 --> 03:32.611
Peace be to God.

03:40.887 --> 03:44.423
Forgive me, Father,
for I have sinned.

03:44.425 --> 03:47.259
It has been six years
since my last confession.

03:47.261 --> 03:48.760
These are my sins.

03:48.762 --> 03:51.530
I've lost my faith.

03:51.532 --> 03:53.632
I've broken the vow of marriage.

03:53.634 --> 03:56.668
I've worked on Sunday.
I've neglected prayer.

03:56.670 --> 04:01.974
I've shown great disrespect to
my parents and family members.

04:01.976 --> 04:04.676
I've abused...

04:04.678 --> 04:08.614
alcohol and drugs a great deal,

04:08.616 --> 04:10.015
and I've enjoyed it.

04:10.017 --> 04:12.484
I've been impatient, angry,

04:12.486 --> 04:15.687
envious, proud, jealous,

04:15.689 --> 04:18.624
revengeful, and lazy.

04:18.625 --> 04:20.524
I have had sex

04:20.527 --> 04:25.664
outside of marriage
countless times.

04:25.666 --> 04:27.599
I've not accepted
God's will for me.

04:29.369 --> 04:32.804
Instead, I've placed my trust
in substitutes for God

04:32.806 --> 04:36.708
and I have despaired of God's mercy.

04:36.710 --> 04:39.911
Can my soul really be saved?

04:39.913 --> 04:43.515
Could you really absolve me
from all of those sins, Father?

04:45.585 --> 04:49.755
What... brought you here today, child?

04:49.757 --> 04:52.958
I saw God yesterday,

04:52.960 --> 04:55.460
and he challenged me to come here.

04:55.462 --> 04:56.695
You saw God.

04:56.697 --> 05:00.032
He came to me through a needle.

05:00.034 --> 05:02.034
God always likes to come inside of me

05:02.036 --> 05:03.935
through large and pointy objects.

05:05.939 --> 05:09.941
Are you a tool of God, Father?

05:09.943 --> 05:13.478
A as the Father sent me, so I send you.

05:13.480 --> 05:16.515
Y you are freed from your sins.
Go in peace.

05:42.842 --> 05:45.110
Did you hire a new housekeeper yet?

05:46.512 --> 05:48.347
No.

05:48.349 --> 05:50.582
Oh, boy.

05:50.584 --> 05:54.619
So, what is it, eggs for
breakfast, lunch, and dinner?

05:56.356 --> 05:59.091
Something like that.

05:59.093 --> 06:00.892
Sometimes I'll make a salad.

06:02.462 --> 06:05.130
The place is probably
a pigsty by now.

06:06.065 --> 06:07.699
It's okay.

06:09.702 --> 06:12.003
I enjoy the solitude.

06:12.005 --> 06:15.374
Well, if you stopped
drinking so much,

06:15.376 --> 06:16.808
