06:25.753 --> 06:28.420
Nobody's perfect.

06:28.422 --> 06:31.790
It's okay to have doubts.

06:32.792 --> 06:34.593
The best ones always do.

06:44.570 --> 06:46.805
My Lord,

06:46.807 --> 06:50.442
