your devoted Julie.

07:17.770 --> 07:21.139
<i>Satan has asked to sift
all of you as wheat.</i>

07:21.141 --> 07:22.641
<i>But I have prayed for you, Peter,</i>

07:22.643 --> 07:24.976
<i>that your faith may not fail.</i>

07:24.978 --> 07:27.338
<i>And when you have turned back,
you strengthen your brothers.</i>

07:28.214 --> 07:31.783
Peter, in answer, said to him,

07:31.785 --> 07:34.586
"Even if all men doubt you,

07:34.588 --> 07:36.655
I will never doubt you."

07:42.028 --> 07:44.729
And Jesus said Peter,

07:44.731 --> 07:48.667
"On this night, before the rooster crows,

07:48.669 --> 07:50.635
