in my head as I was climaxing.

08:48.562 --> 08:50.795
Then I thought of you.

08:50.797 --> 08:52.297
Those eyes.

08:52.299 --> 08:55.934
What are they? Green? Hazel?

09:00.673 --> 09:04.209
