15:03.003 --> 15:05.637
In the house of the Lord,
no one stays invisible.

15:07.506 --> 15:09.574
You mind if we take a look?

15:09.576 --> 15:12.610
Go ahead.

15:19.486 --> 15:21.653
Are you a Catholic?

15:24.189 --> 15:26.925
