19:53.326 --> 19:54.926
How do I know it's yours?

19:56.461 --> 19:58.763
That day I came to you for help,

19:58.765 --> 20:01.699
I decided to turn my life around.

20:01.701 --> 20:03.834
I promised myself
no more cheap thrills.

20:03.836 --> 20:05.937
Just life.

20:08.340 --> 20:10.808
But I know I'm not fit
to keep this child, so I...

20:10.810 --> 20:12.410
I'll leave today.

20:12.412 --> 20:15.346
I I promise I'll try
to pay you back somehow.

20:15.348 --> 20:17.548
No, I... don't.

20:24.957 --> 20:26.591
We'll leave together.

20:28.460 --> 20:31.329
I'm really not fit for this anymore.

20:31.331 --> 20:33.264
No, no, no, it's complicated.

20:33.266 --> 20:34.365
