What's complicated?

20:34.367 --> 20:35.600
They're gonna come after us.

20:35.602 --> 20:37.001
I still owe them money.

20:50.916 --> 20:52.516
How much?

20:54.920 --> 20:56.787
Twenty grand.

21:04.663 --> 21:06.564
Take this.

21:06.566 --> 21:09.667
Get yourself a room at the motel
next to the train station.

21:09.669 --> 21:12.837
We'll go first thing in the
morning and settle your debt.

21:12.839 --> 21:14.272
I I can't do this.

21:14.274 --> 21:15.740
Yes, you can, and you will.

21:40.532 --> 21:43.067
<i>Son of a bitch.</i>

21:43.069 --> 21:44.869
