21:50.476 --> 21:51.876
<i>I'll give you a bonus, I suppose.</i>

21:55.347 --> 21:57.782
Burn it all down.

21:57.784 --> 21:58.883
Save yourself.

22:47.567 --> 22:50.368
<i>Burn it all down.</i>

22:50.370 --> 22:52.036
<i>Save yourself.</i>

23:23.568 --> 23:25.503
<i>Are you committed?</i>

24:49.488 --> 24:53.157
I think you are beyond saving.

24:53.159 --> 24:56.727
You've got friends in high places.

24:56.729 --> 24:59.597
That's the only reason you are here.

24:59.599 --> 25:02.967
But if your friends
think this is what you need,

25:02.969 --> 25:06.036
I'll show you the time of your life.

25:26.559 --> 25:30.661
Welcome to Monastero Saligia.

26:34.759 --> 26:36.026
Wake up.

26:40.366 --> 26:42.700
What did you do to her?

26:57.350 --> 27:00.384
I'm not sure what I find
more troubling,

27:00.386 --> 27:03.754
