with a crucifix.

27:32.652 --> 27:33.751
Classic.

27:33.753 --> 27:35.119
I'm serious.

27:35.121 --> 27:36.887
Hmm.

27:44.329 --> 27:46.263
What was that all about?

27:47.165 --> 27:48.298
Vatican Intelligence.

27:56.909 --> 27:59.443
Prego, senor.

27:59.445 --> 28:01.211
Grazie.

28:04.949 --> 28:08.085
