don't you think?

28:13.059 --> 28:15.726
Say what you will
about good old Benito,

28:15.728 --> 28:20.030
but he truly understood
the essence of religion.

28:20.032 --> 28:21.198
Who?

28:21.200 --> 28:22.933
Mussolini.

28:22.935 --> 28:24.234
Il Duce.

28:26.371 --> 28:27.905
If it wasn't for him,

28:27.907 --> 28:30.007
the Vatican wouldn't have its own state,

28:30.009 --> 28:33.277
and you would be rotting
in jail right now.

28:33.279 --> 28:37.014
Aggravated arson, hate crime.

28:37.016 --> 28:38.782
Ten years, I would say.

28:40.385 --> 28:41.885
It's a nice thought,

28:41.887 --> 28:43.887
owing your freedom to a dictator.

28:43.889 --> 28:47.291
Is that why you tried to kill yourself?

28:47.293 --> 28:50.094
You thought it would set you free.

28:50.096 --> 28:52.429
Because I got to tell you,

28:52.431 --> 28:55.833
there are much better reasons
on this God's earth,

28:55.835 --> 28:57.735
