sword, or a crucifix.

30:14.979 --> 30:17.181
Silence implies consent.

30:17.183 --> 30:19.082
Now, who's driving?
The other padre?

30:19.084 --> 30:21.051
Indeed. Orange juice, please.

30:21.053 --> 30:23.020
Oh, sure.

30:23.022 --> 30:26.156
The stories they tell of you,
they are no exaggeration.

30:26.158 --> 30:29.193
Sure they are.

30:29.195 --> 30:31.195
And if Jesus was alive today,

30:31.197 --> 30:33.564
