to the Eternal City?

30:45.511 --> 30:48.846
Okay, I think it's best
if we move to a table.

30:48.848 --> 30:50.080
Yeah.

30:50.082 --> 30:52.416
Okay.

30:52.418 --> 30:54.885
I'm just screwing with you boys.

