been excommunicated.

31:14.874 --> 31:17.507
It's starting to feel
inevitable, Charlie.

31:17.509 --> 31:19.409
Hmm.

31:19.411 --> 31:21.979
You're a good man.

31:21.981 --> 31:24.548
